      "layout": "The site uses a full-bleed, max-width layout, centered with no strong page margins. The hero section is simply a continuation of the data table, presenting personal information in a similar grid. Sections are defined by dense data tables, separated by `73px` vertical spacing. Content is arranged in columns, creating a dense, scannable data grid with clear `1px` borders. Global navigation is a minimalist top bar, integrating seamlessly into the grid structure.",
